OK. Something's happened with Yahoo and the reply to Yanshosh's reply to 
Desmonus hasn't gotten through, so here it is again.
And please don't mind spelling mistakes, I have to type quickly.

* Desmonus simply ignored the fact that both of the males on either side of 
her glared at each other as she took hold of their hands.
Finding herself a bit annoyed at it.
Greedy, was her thoughts. Most likely trying to make sure that they had her 
to themselves instead of simply getting along for the moment.
But their greed she could use more then anybot could think, and she was 
indeed going to use it.

She looked towards Bloodystrike as he began to jabber on about his quarters, 
catching on right awat at just why his room was the first place he wanted 
for her to check out.
He was fairly blunt...without getting right to the point right away.
But she followed him anyway, simply thinking how these bots could be pleased 
so easily with such simple pleasures where all she was after was a meal.
And there was one on each side of her. Dinner and Desert...
But she would do what she had to to feed, as long as she could survive and 
live she cared little for what pleasures they asked of her, something so 
trivial that it didn't even concern her.

Desmonus then found herself being pulled in another direction by Reptilica, 
but both simply in the same line of direction....
So, he wanted her to see his quarters as well?
She sighed, such simple things for such simple minds.
But then they were at it again, arguing with each other over who's quarters 
were better.
Men!
Desmonus simply took hold of their hands more firmly and cleared her 
throat.*

" Hmm...perhaps it is not wise to tour on such empty stomachs, perhaps a 
small meal is in order before we continue towards the more formal subjects. 
Besides, I wouldn't minding getting to know you two a little better.
If one does not know thri team mates then one does not know themselves.
Oh! And I forgot to introduce myself. My name is Desmonus..."

* She simply spoke, giving their hands a little extra squeeze.*
